{"tid":412872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【「殺無赦」風波】范太指是語言暴力　料集會氣氛影響　毋須逐一計較","createTime":"2017-09-25T04:44:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T14:45:39.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fff9535e7cfcf9da1342237f17957cce62d7b2ae","tid":412872,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170925/s00001/279113db929560acbe93d1dd08faba17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F279113db929560acbe93d1dd08faba17.jpg&h=cd929216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會議員何君堯「殺無赦」言論風波持續，全國人大常委范徐麗泰認為有關言論是「語言暴力」，但指何君堯當時可能受集會氣氛影響，不應只拿他一人做例子， 也無必要逐一計較，重申希望政治人物言論要理性。<br />\n<br />\n事緣屏山鄉事委員會主席曾樹和早前在一個反「港獨」集會上，發表「殺」言論，何君堯則附和「無赦」，引起爭議。 范徐麗泰昨會晤記者時表示，該言論屬語言暴力，強調不論政見如何，都應避免語言暴力，「建不建制派，是否反對派根本不重要，重要的是香港不應該，盡量不要有言語暴力」。<br />\n<br />\n不過范徐麗泰說，何君堯言論可能受集會氣氛影響，認為不應只拿他一人做例子，也無必要逐一計較。她又說，自己不需要勸對方收回言論，因為要提出有關建議的人應是立法會議員和香港建制人士，「我不是香港建制人士，我在香港是一介市民，是一介市民的意見」。<br />\n<br />\n至於有關言論會否違背特首林鄭月娥提出修補社會撕裂的主張，范徐麗泰稱，不應該將林鄭月娥和所有建制派視作一樣，強調任何建制派人士所做的事，與特區政府是兩回事。<br />\n<br />\n全國政協委員、民建聯前主席譚耀宗昨回應稱，非法「佔中」等議題的確令人反感，認為表達意見並無問題，但一個人有時說話不準確，如一時太激動講出不準確字眼，就會被人抽秤。他相信何君堯會汲取經驗和教訓，他不宜太多鞭撻。<br />\n<br />\n行政會議成員湯家驊則希望何君堯「知恥自重」，指香港作為文明多元化社會，不應用侮辱言詞攻擊政治對手，「身為律師應該尊重自己」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506309698098\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506309698098&d=%2BEgXdx1jySSNsqNy2%2FN8WU%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=76a00ada\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170925%2Fs00001%2F1506309698098&h=e757221a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170925/s00001/1506309698098</a>"},{"pid":"c1353a6e74d210f7330f486f2569c80904a20730","tid":412872,"uid":149361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"痴撚線"},{"pid":"051cba59e68c36d6294fffea53442193a5d9784b","tid":412872,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:53:31.000Z","msg":"拎埋曾樹和祭旗囉咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e382a347e791634c8ed3a1117dadde828d1c457b","tid":412872,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:55:33.000Z","msg":"呢個人冇乜影響力啦，忽略"},{"pid":"1575225a4262e40f8fdcbebd1bdde7646c717a0b","tid":412872,"uid":26752,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:57:58.000Z","msg":"建國後犯婦人必需要上斷頭台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c428e7f583197114c0ca903b4fe0bb368db7374","tid":412872,"uid":17878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T04:58:03.000Z","msg":"想大事化小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea6fdc1dc4e4aa80b137a6207c01c12e24a683c","tid":412872,"uid":4942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:15:38.000Z","msg":"雙重標準 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be08e6204cd0578aade19da1c5cb1001449722fe","tid":412872,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T05:16:20.000Z","msg":"又冰山一角事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76cf6db3bc12f9a52a517fc73662e62ff6d40e21","tid":412872,"uid":37524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢個人冇乜影響力啦，忽略</blockquote><br />\n所以成日響度鳩嗡"},{"pid":"64697ed413ab77c2c55ac201d71b6ab4f75e69a6","tid":412872,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T11:24:19.000Z","msg":"屌你祖宗十八代<br />\n<br />\n個奪字都要坐，殺字又冇事。<br />\n<br />\n你不如話香港已經冇法治只有人治，大家會順氣啲。"},{"pid":"6d1b1f068a0faf2194071ec2f768268124e3d298","tid":412872,"uid":19353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:23:44.000Z","msg":"以前每年都會loop黃子華嘅秋前算帳幾次 近年已經冇睇 因為而家每一日都發生緊黃子華講嘅野 再睇亦唔會笑得出"},{"pid":"e3db3b4a7bb0e30f3e5a8740d724e9a611724c53","tid":412872,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdc310a9249a495ed8088ea4f7110cf13da4cb2","tid":412872,"uid":129111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:19:46.000Z","msg":"幾時先肯死"},{"pid":"5a986b25360106de22e7b17c324f9c067e06ca65","tid":412872,"uid":55597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:27:16.000Z","msg":"無必要逐一計較，咁咪全部拉晒返去<br />\n<br />\n曾樹和同何君堯受現場氣氛影響而講個 殺無赦<br />\n咁現場其他集會人士可能受殺無赦影響真係落手殺人<br />\n咁即係而家香港好多潛在殺人犯，最好全部都拉晒先"},{"pid":"2660ce81857ce459742a57cdc8db994a8891b05f","tid":412872,"uid":46947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:37:41.000Z","msg":"大快活邊位巴打今朝一路食早餐一路用刀篤腸仔一路大大聲嗌&ldquo;殺無赦&rdquo;呀？<br />\n嚇撚到個個彈開幾張枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"041e7e287037ca6a59cc1b6da774af78dac80b54","tid":412872,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T14:38:46.000Z","msg":"黃之鋒都係同樣原因姐，但要坐監喎，唔見你咁講喎范太"},{"pid":"4b2d7a06bd41686950e5858ab45929e67992e23e","tid":412872,"uid":11753,"like":0,"disl